The following example show how to build a CacheManagerConfiguration and then
using the CacheFactory to create a new cache manager instance.


var cache = CacheFactory.Build(typeof(string), "myCacheName", settings =>
{
   settings
       .WithUpdateMode(CacheUpdateMode.Up)
       .WithDictionaryHandle()
           .EnablePerformanceCounters()
           .WithExpiration(ExpirationMode.Sliding, TimeSpan.FromSeconds(10));
});

